name: Tiger Mastery Slate
description: Struck to recognize your achievement in reaching the rank of 19 - Tiger.

languages.description: Coniata per riconoscere il tuo successo nel raggiungere il grado 19 - Tigre.

languages.description: 랭크 19 - 타이거에 도달한 업적을 기리기 위한 표창패입니다.

languages.description: Impresionado por reconocer tu logro al alcanzar el rango 19 - Tigre.

languages.name: กระดานชนวนความเชี่ยวชาญ: เสือ
